Senator Ali Modu Sheriff has expressed shock over the demise of Senator Teslim Folarin’s wife. Condoling with Folarin, the Senator representing Oyo Central Senatorial District over wife’s transition to higher glory, Sheriff said that the death of Chief (Barr.) Angela Nwaka Folarin came to him as a rude shock. Sheriff, in a statement, said: “The news of the passing on of your beloved wife Chief (Barr.) Angela Nwaka Folarin, who transited to higher glory in the United Kingdom came to me as a rude shock, especially as she was in sound health before her demise Ajimobi Commiserates With Folarin Over Wife’s Death Boko Haram Stopped Us From Giving Buhari 2million Votes –… “I know this must be a very trying period for you and your entire family, knowing how well you bond with her and the love she had for you and your family. “However, death is a necessity for all mortals, our prayers are that we fulfill our days on earth and work to impact lives positively, which I know your wife did, haven known her over the years. “As I share in your pains and grief at this period of your loss, I implore you to be strong and steadfast in Allah from where cometh our help. “Your wife was indeed an exceptional person, a woman of valor with a large heart and will be greatly missed by all, especially those whose lives she touched positivity in one way or the other.”